<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 31 at 4:13AM EDT  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Gusty winds this morning...
Southwest winds of 15 to 25 mph will persist this morning west of
Interstate 69. While wind gusts of 30 to 40 mph will be common, a
few locations could see brief gusts to around 45 mph. The highest
gusts are expected to subside from west to east through 7 am EDT.</description>
